The paper deals with image compositing, which is a task related to computer vision and graphics. The use of instance segmentation and image matting processes suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, the paper may also belong to the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category as it deals with image editing and compositing. The use of machine learning techniques such as deep learning suggests that the paper may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
